---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="projects | alpblkba">
  <h1>projects</h1>

  <p>
    A small collection of hardware-aware systems work: FPGA prototypes, computer architecture
    experiments, embedded labs, and low-level software utilities.
  </p>

  <section>
    <h2>hardware / fpga / architecture</h2>

    <div class="card-grid">
      <article class="card">
        <h3>rv32i-mla</h3>
        <p>
          RV32I CPU and accelerator experiments on PYNQ, written in Verilog.
          Focused on simple processor design, memory-mapped interfaces, and
          hardware/software integration.
        </p>
        <a href="https://github.com/alpblkba/rv32i-mla">repository</a>
      </article>

      <article class="card">
        <h3>hardware-security</h3>
        <p>
          FPGA-based hardware security tasks, PUF experiments, and low-level
          security concepts, mostly written in Verilog.
        </p>
        <a href="https://github.com/alpblkba/hardware-security">repository</a>
      </article>

      <article class="card">
        <h3>fpga-programming</h3>
        <p>
          FPGA programming experiments and digital design practice, focused on
          Verilog, synthesis flow, board bring-up, and hardware debugging.
        </p>
        <a href="https://github.com/alpblkba/fpga-programming">repository</a>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>software / systems utilities</h2>

    <div class="card-grid">
      <article class="card">
        <h3>iot-lab</h3>
        <p>
          Embedded systems lab work with STM32, C/C++, UART/GPIO bring-up,
          device-level debugging, and practical board interaction.
        </p>
        <a href="https://github.com/alpblkba/iot-lab">repository</a>
      </article>

      <article class="card">
        <h3>promon</h3>
        <p>
          Tiny low-level process monitor targeting Windows, Linux, and macOS,
          written in C/C++ with a focus on system-level process inspection.
        </p>
        <a href="https://github.com/alpblkba/promon">repository</a>
      </article>

      <article class="card">
        <h3>alppad</h3>
        <p>
          A simple, minimalistic text editor application built with C++17 and
          the Qt framework.
        </p>
        <a href="https://github.com/alpblkba/alppad">repository</a>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <p>
    <a href="/">← home</a>
  </p>
</BaseLayout>